title: South Carolina Disaster Recovery Centers Open in Darlington and Orangeburg Counties (FEMA - Federal Emergency ...
text: ( Source : FEMA - Federal Emergency Management Agency ) COLUMBIA, S.C. - Two disaster recovery centers are now open in Darlington and Orangeburg to help South Carolina flood survivors. The centers' hours are 8 a.m. to 7 p.m. seven days a week
